########################################################################

@NODE INTRO "Introduction"

   @{b}Introduction :@{ub}

      F-bench is a File Director with a program manager.

      It's Many Features Include:

          -  20 Differents Types Files are detected by F-bench :

                  * IFF/ILBM Picture
                  * IFF/Animation IFF (ANIM5 Format)
                  * GIF Picture
                  * JPEG Picture
                  * BMP Picture
                  * PCX Picture
                  * FLI/FLC Animation
                  * Executable Amiga
                  * Executable PC
                  * Text (ASCII)
                  * AmigaGuide
                  * LHA Archive
                  * DMS Archive
                  * LZX Archive
                  * IFF/8SVX Sample
                  * WAVE Sample
                  * Protracker Module
                  * Octamed Module
                  * Workbench Icon
                  * Powerpacked File

          -  Preferences Editor : Fonts, Screen Mode, File Configuration
                                  And Language.

          -  System Compliant, Fully Multitasking, Very Compatiable.

          -  Asynchronous Multitasking.

          -  Easy-To-Use.

          -  Include A Program Manager.


                     @{b}NOTE: F-Bench Distributed As Shareware.@{b}


@ENDNODE

